Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:06.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}怪獣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:06.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right, it's so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:08.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}珍獣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:08.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I merely need to fix him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}財宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I only need the power to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The question is how we will manage to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:16.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}魔境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:16.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If anyone has any brilliant ideas, \NI'd like to hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}秘境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're simply awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:27.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「未知」という言葉が放つ魔力 その力に魅せられた すごい奴らがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:27.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When you asked us to join, did you not \Nalready have an answer in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人は　彼らを…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We exterminate the Ants \Nin silence, one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ハンター」と呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come on, what are you doing? You'll never defeat Knuckle and Shoot, \Nmuch less the Chimera Ants, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:21.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」によって封印されていた 箱の中には 謎のアイテムが３つ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:21.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Promise x And x Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:45.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　やっぱり　お前も ハンターになっちまったか。 これが　親父の声… [ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　それで　１つ 聞きたいことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:45.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As the Queen prepares for the King's birth, she requires the equivalent of two hundred \Nand fifty human meatballs per day to give birth to a strong King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:59.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　会う気があるなら このまま聞いてくれ。 [ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　もし　その気がないなら 停止ボタンを押せばいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:59.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:14.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　イエスってことか それじゃ　もう一度　聞くぜ。 [ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　覚悟は　あるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:14.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}continue their training so they \Ncan defeat Knuckle and Shoot, take their tokens, and return to NGL.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:49.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　はぁ…　そんなに会いたいか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:49.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will this really be enough for \Nthem to execute the plan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:56.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　俺は　お前に会いたくない。 [ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　どの面　下げて会えばいいのか 分からねえしな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:56.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to slaughter Morel's disciples?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　ろくなもんじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:14.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　俺が　これを吹き込んでから お前が聞くことになる日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:14.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You finally lasted for three hours. We did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:19.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最低１０年以上の時を 経ているだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:19.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was hard! I can't move an inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:24.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　だが　その間 絶対に変わらないものがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:24.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What are you talking about? Stand up. We're going out. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:33.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　俺が　俺であることだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:33.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wh-Why? See? You can move. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:38.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ボ！ ボォ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:38.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tell us why we're going to see Knuckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ボォ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Jeez, don't ask questions \Nwith obvious answers. To fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:51.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　だから　お前が このテープを聞いている今も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:51.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What are you talking about? We still have time. What if we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:55.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どこかでバカをやっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:55.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You just try again. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　それでも会いたきゃ 捜してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whether you win or lose isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:02.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　だが　さっきも言ったが 俺は　お前とは会いたくねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:02.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All that matters is who ends \Nup with the tokens, right? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:07.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　近づくのが分かったら とんずら　かますぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:07.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means you must take theirs. If it looks like you'll lose, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:11.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　捕まえてみろよ お前もハンターなんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:11.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then try again the next day. From here on, you'll practice \NRen for three hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:40.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　聞きたければ このまま聞いてくれ。 [ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　別に　いいなら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:40.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Still a no show, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいのか？ うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your owner's really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:48.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　もしかしたら　何か 手掛かりがあるかもしれないぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:48.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ないよ　多分　勘だけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That tickles. Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:58.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それに言ったろ？ 俺の母親は　ミトさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:58.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:22.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えぇ!?　デッキにオーラが!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:22.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is that Knuckle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」だ！ 「念」でテープを巻き戻してる！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:32.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」？　まさか　今どこかで!? 違う　「念」を込めたんだよ １０年以上前に。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:32.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:37.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}停止ボタンを押したら 巻き戻すように。 何で？ さぁな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:37.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're the other candidates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:52.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか　消す気だ　自分の声を！ えぇ!? ダメだ　止められない！　クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:52.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Guess they must not respect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:07:01.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダメだ　止まらねえ！ コンセント抜いたのに!? 悪いな　ゴン　壊すぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:07:01.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I'm being compared to a couple of kids, they must not think I'm very strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:08.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クソ！　ダメだ！ 「念」でガードしてやがる！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:08.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Such an intimidating presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:29.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}終わったみたいだね。 はぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:29.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Were you just out swimming or something, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　今度は　録音ボタンが入った！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You kids can never defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱ　ダビング用のテープも やられてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}S-Stupid... Wh-Why would I cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で　ここまでする必要が あったのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not upset about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}手掛かりを残したくなかった ってことだろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Th-Th-These are just, well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}手掛かりって？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tears from laughing too much, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:01.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}音声からだけでも 相当のデータが得られるんだ。 そうなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:01.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll kill you, get it? So don't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:07.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}録音した人間の身長や体重 性別　年齢　顔のつくり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:07.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Punch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}持病も分かるし 心理状態だって読み取れる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? I'll show you how much stronger I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:17.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}へぇ。 背景の雑音から　録音した場所も 特定できることもあるしな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:17.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And you'll realize that I don't need \Nto bother dodging your punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　警戒したのは もっと別のことだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hit me as many times as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:24.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}別なことって？ 念能力だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:24.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if I don't take a step from this spot, leave your tokens behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}機械より はるかに優秀な解析ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is the best chance you'll have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:32.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}念能力の持ち主がいても おかしくないだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:32.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You kids would need a hundred years \Nbefore you could try fighting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:39.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}例えば　声を聞いただけで 相手の全てが分かる能力とか。 そうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:39.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're the one who challenged us to a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の親父　手ごわいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't look down on us! I'd like to respond that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:48.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。 それにしても　テープが ダメになっちまったから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:48.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it's clear that we aren't on Knuckle's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}手掛かりは ２つになっちまったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We have no right to argue that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:57.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}指輪と　ロムカードか。 指輪は　ともかく 問題は　このロムカードだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:57.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Not right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:03.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　これ　普通のより小さいね。 これ専用のハードがあるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:03.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The fact is, we can't overcome everything with willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『ジョイステ』？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We can't argue with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:16.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『ジョイステーション』って ゲーム機　３世代前の。 お前　なんも知らねえのな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:16.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But we don't have to accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:24.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きっと　あるぜ おもちゃ屋って　あるか？ うん　あるけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:24.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't stop hitting you until you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし　待ってろ。 え？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Enough talk... Just get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あら　どこ行くの？ おもちゃ屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First comes rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:38.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}港の外れだよ！ 分かってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:38.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whoa, whoa, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気をつけてね！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's with the intense aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}へぇ これが『ジョイステーション』。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I guess wrong, I could die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:04.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}懐かしいな　昔よくやったぜ 隠れた名作も　いっぱいあるし。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:04.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come on... I'd expect him to attack the belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:09.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふん このロムカードも名作なのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:09.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, that's the only real choice. Gotta be the belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}タイトルとか何も書いてないけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rock... Yeah, it's the belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:15.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前　本当に ゲームやったことないんだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:15.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Belly! Belly! Belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}貴重な奴。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう？ これはゲームソフトじゃ　ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:46.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうやら　入ってるゲームは １つだけだな。 『グリードアイランド』って ゲームらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:46.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Knuckle-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:11:02.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それにしても すごいデータ量だぜ。 無駄だと思うけど 一応　データをコピーしとくぜ。 [TV]　『グリードアイランド』をコピーします。 さて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:11:02.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I... trusted... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:11.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ネットだよ ゲーム名が分かったんだ。 売ってる店を検索する。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:11.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:15.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}え！　１件もないのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:15.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Obviously, he's a total idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:33.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}つまり　個人が作ったゲームでさ もともと　売り物じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:33.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:38.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何かの事情で　発売禁止に なってるゲームってことさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:38.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're stronger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とにかく調べてみるか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Guess I underestimated you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:52.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「『グリードアイランド』 ハンター専用　ハンティングゲーム」。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:52.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why didn't you take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:12:00.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハンター専用？ しかも　何だ　この値段！ ５億８０００万!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:12:00.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should've taken the \Ntoken and ditched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５８億だ！ えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We don't want your token.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:09.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しっかし　何ちゅう でたらめな値段なんだ。 販売個数は１００個だって これって　多くないよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:09.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We want the strength to defeat \Nyou in a straight-up fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:14.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すっげぇ少ねえよ ぜってぇナメてる　少な過ぎるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:14.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Could I ask you something? Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}けど　分かった 値段は　とんでもねえけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why did you become a Beast Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハンターなら買える値段だし こりゃ　完全な売り切れだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? It's a long story...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}制作元に　在庫は　ないのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And it brings back bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうだな 一応　問い合わせてみるか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:27.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, why did you volunteer for the punitive force?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:33.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL] お尋ねのソフトですが そちらは　もう 絶版になっております。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:33.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Simply put, to keep it from doing its job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　申し訳ありませんが 再生産の予定もございません。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't like the idea of cutting off \Nwhatever doesn't fit the mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうですか　どうも。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My teacher says I'm just a softy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:48.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱりダメだった。 うん　持ってる人を捜し出して 譲ってもらうしかないのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:48.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But you can't judge something that \Nyou've never seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:51.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だな　ネットの逆オークションに 告知して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:51.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First, you have to exchange blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}売ってくれる奴が名乗り出るのを 待つってのがセオリーだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And you'll get yourself killed in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:03.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}闘技場で稼いだ金 ２人合わせても８億くらいか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:03.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're a good kid. Now that we've fought, I see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あと５０億かぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You, too. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:19.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}市場価格より　高い金を 要求されるなんてザラだもん。 じゃあ　もっと高いってこと？ かもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:19.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You! He wouldn't leave your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:25.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。 うん。 まぁ　ダメもとで 告知だけしとこうよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:25.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They say good Hunters are well-liked by animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}値段　要相談」。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}S-Stupid! I'm not crying... Don't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:02.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}額が額だから 考えてみりゃ　当たり前か。 お手上げだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:02.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Morel's student...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:10.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これ　一つ一つとなんて 交渉してられねえぞ。 第一　本物か偽物かも 俺達じゃ　判断つかねえし。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:10.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:20.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}情報も豊富になるけど 俺も　あんま詳しくねえしなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:20.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Fight me any time you want. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:24.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームやネットに詳しい人って 誰か　いないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:24.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll give you as many tries as you want. But it's impossible for you to beat me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:29.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…　いた　両方　詳しい奴。 えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:29.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}in the twenty days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ　本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:56.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今？　どこでもいいだろ。 お前に言うと　おふくろに 伝わるかもしんないし。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:56.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:08.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヤダよ 出掛けてるって言っとけよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:08.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:12.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウソつけよ　あいつが 外出するわけねえじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:12.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:17.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}てめぇのフィギュア 全部　ぶっ壊すって伝えてよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:17.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's begin, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かったよ　つなげろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? Chiona's squadron is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　キル！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:27.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言っとくけど　俺のコレクションに 指一本でも触れたら　殺すぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:27.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is it similar to what happened \Nto Reikei's squadron? It appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:33.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}冗談だよ　兄貴 怒んないでよ　怖いなぁ。 兄貴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:33.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The leader disappeared first, and then the rest vanished, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それで？　何なんだ？ 忙しいのに　もう！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, that is the logical conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』？ ああ　知ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We've been cutting down on \Nthe number of soldiers, and our prey has begun to scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の口から　そんなレアゲームの 名前が出るとは思わなかったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If humans target us during an extended hunt, it could be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:56.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}持ってないのか？ [TEL]　ああ　持ってない 欲しかったけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:56.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should we ask the Queen to move the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:00.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}発売当時　俺　５歳だぜ 金なかったし。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:00.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, we can't trouble the Queen right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:05.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１００本限定の販売に　申し込みが ２万件以上あったらしいぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:05.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then we ask Neferpitou-dono to investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:12.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５８億ジェニーの 現金一括販売のみだったのにさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:12.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That idea doesn't thrill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:21.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}持ち主さえ特定できない。 いろんな意味で伝説のゲームだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:21.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll let you handle things outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:25.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　で　何？ お前　もしかして探してんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:25.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll protect the inside of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:30.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁね。 [TEL]　無理　無理　やめとけよ 俺でさえ諦めたんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:30.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll try to strengthen this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:35.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}へぇ　兄貴が手も足も出ないで 降参してんのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:35.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just as I expected... Well, at least she doesn't issue \Nany strange orders on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:40.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フン　昔の話だよ 今は心当たりくらいあるさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:40.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We should start by determining \Nour current troop strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:46.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ただ　労力と金額を考えると そこまでして欲しいゲームでも ないしなってことだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:46.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How many Squadron Leaders remain? Assuming Chiona was taken out, twenty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:54.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふん その心当たりってのを教えてよ。 [TEL]　はぁ？　タダじゃ　イヤだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:54.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Each Squadron Leader has four or five officers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:59.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』のメモリーカードと交換 ってのは　どう？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:59.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And each officer commands \Nten to fifteen soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:07.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どういうことだ？ [TEL]　ちょっとしたコネでさ ロムカードだけ手に入れたんだよ。 [TEL]　兄貴なら このデータを解析して
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:07.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Some squadrons are under tight control, but many are free to wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:13.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ソフト自体　再生することも できるんじゃないの？ その話　本当だろうな？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:13.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The missing four squadrons fall \Nunder the latter category...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:17.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　取引でウソつくほど 俗ぼけしてねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:17.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Of the remaining squadrons, \Nover half lack discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　分かった 心当たりは２つある。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And none will heed a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:27.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちょっと待った ケータイじゃ　ヤバいだろ？ 安心しろよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:27.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They've become arrogant since learning Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:31.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}盗聴されたって　そいつが どうこうできるレベルじゃ　ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:31.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then we could use them to lay a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ…　ああ　そうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sure that's what's currently going \Nthrough the enemy's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ＯＫ　分かった　ロムカードは いつもの方法で送る。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, we should be able to \Ncontinue the current plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:47.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}悪ぃ！　話の流れでカードのコピーと 交換ってことにしちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:47.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Knov and I will be able to tell \Nonce a trap has been laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:54.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　構わないよ　コピーだったら。 その代わり ２つの有力情報を得たぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:54.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In fact, I believe we should \Nspring a few of those traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:18:02.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず　１つ。 ハンターだけがアクセスできる ハンター専用サイトがある。 そこなら『グリードアイランド』の 手掛かりもあるだろうって。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:18:02.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hmm? If we ignore the disciplined squads, they'll band together and cause us problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:06.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか！ ハンターライセンスを使うんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:06.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Most likely, they'll start pairing disciplined and undisciplined squads together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:15.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バカ！　自宅のパソコンを使ったら 住所がバレバレになるだろ！ ハンターライセンス狙いの小悪党が ぞろぞろ　島に集まっちまうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:15.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we launch an indiscriminate \Nattack, it will result in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:21.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　そっか。 こういうのは　公共のパソコン使って やるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:21.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We should be able to eliminate \Nanother three or four squads
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホテルとか　ネットカフェとか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}before the enemy tries another approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　何にせよ　アドレスが まだ分からないけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can already see their next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:35.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}兄貴にロムカードを送れば 教えてくれる約束だ。 んで　もう１つが ヨークシンシティでのオークション。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:35.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If all goes well, we'll finish up \Nbefore reinforcements arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えぇ!? ヨークシンシティっていったら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hope
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう　クラピカ　レオリオと 再会を約束した場所。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}things go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:52.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}兄貴は　ガセかもって 言ってたけど ある人物が そのゲームを何十本も
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:52.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, three hours! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:59.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今年の　そのオークションに流す って情報があるらしい。 もしかして　その人物がジンかも。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:59.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, then... Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:07.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ　そう考えると あながち　ガセじゃないかもな。 手に入れるためには 莫大な　お金が必要だね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:07.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そういうこったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What, there are more of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:16.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いずれにせよ 俺達は ヨークシンシティに行く運命だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:16.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't hold back... Help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:49.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クリアデータ入りのロムカードに ５００億の懸賞金を懸けてるのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:49.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's on, Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさに　伝説だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフン　面白い。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll take you both on at once! I won't say a word about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が伝説に終止符を打ってやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}how you're condescending to us... We're more than happy to accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:06.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ　すっごい　ご馳走だね 何かあったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:06.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's go, Killua! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それじゃあ！ いっただきます！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have no time to waste playing \Naround with you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:21:06.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ミトさん 俺　必ず　ジンを見つけるから！ ジンに会ったら また島に戻って来るからね！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:21:06.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once they've accomplished \Nthe tough task before them, they'll gain a confidence boost \Nthat will spur their growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それまで元気でね！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, to complete that task, \Nthey must defeat me! And that ain't gonna happen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:35.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この後は　ゴンと…。 キルアの…。 ジンは　自分に会いたければ 捜してみろと言い　謎を残した この後は　ゴンと…。 キルアの…。 ハンサイクロペディア！ ジンは　自分に会いたければ 捜してみろと言い　謎を残した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:35.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Given his personality, he's probably already warmed \Nto these opponents...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:44.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジンは　自分に会いたければ 捜してみろと言い　謎を残した ゴンは　その謎を解き 父親に会うため 再び故郷を離れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:44.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I doubt he'd sell me out, but it's probable that he'll accidentally \Nsay something he shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:49.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアと共に　ヨークシンシティへ 向かったのだった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:49.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My chance will come after they leave.
